<!DOCTYPE qhelp SYSTEM "qhelp.dtd">
<qhelp>
  <overview>
    <p>Route loaders that read search params need matching <code>validateSearch</code> and <code>loaderDeps</code> declarations.</p>
  </overview>
  <recommendation>
    <p>Normalize search params in <code>validateSearch</code>, copy the same normalized values into <code>loaderDeps</code>, and use <code>deps</code> inside the loader.</p>
  </recommendation>
</qhelp>
